"जाएं, :guilabel:`SOAP IF सेटिंग` तक स्क्रॉल करें, और सुनिश्चित करें कि :guilabel:`सेशन "
"मोड` और :guilabel:`Occupy मोड` दोनों :guilabel:`एनेबल` पर सेट हैं।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:65
msgid ""
"If **a dedicated user** has been set up on the cash machine for Odoo, which "
