msgstr ""
":menuselection:`पॉइंट ऑफ़ सेल --> प्रॉडक्ट --> प्रॉडक्ट` पर जाएं और :guilabel:`नया` "
"क्लिक करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:101
msgid "Enter a product name."
msgstr "प्रॉडक्ट का नाम दर्ज करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:102
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Combo` and select the "
