msgstr ""
":guilabel:`प्रॉडक्ट टाइप` को :guilabel:`कॉम्बो` पर सेट करें और संबंधित :ref:`कॉम्बो "
"च्वाइसेज़ <pos/products/combo-choices>` को चुनें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:104
msgid "Add a :guilabel:`Sales Price`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`सेल्स प्राइस` जोड़ें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:105
msgid ""
"Optionally, click the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` tab to select the "
