msgstr "कॉम्बो ऐप्लिकेशन"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:115
msgid "To apply combos, follow these steps:"
msgstr "कॉम्बो लागू करने के लिए, इन स्टेप्स को फ़ॉलो करें:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:117
msgid "Open the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-register>`."
msgstr ":ref:`पीओएस रजिस्टर <pos/use/open-register>` खोलें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:118
msgid ""
"Click the desired product combo, and select the preferred items for each "
"combo choice."
msgstr ""
"वांछित प्रॉडक्ट कॉम्बो पर क्लिक करें, और प्रत्येक कॉम्बो च्वाइस के लिए पसंदीदा आइटम चुनें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:119
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Add to order`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`ऑर्डर में जोड़ें` पर क्लिक करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:120
