":guilabel:`Payment`: Process the direct payment for the selected product(s)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`पेमेंट`: चयनित प्रॉडक्ट के लिए डायरेक्ट पेमेंट प्रोसेस करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:375
msgid ":guilabel:`Split Order`: Create a sub-order."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Split Order`: एक सब-ऑर्डर बनाएं।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:376
msgid ":guilabel:`Transfer`: Transfer one or all products to another table."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ट्रांसफ़र`: एक या सभी प्रॉडक्ट को दूसरी टेबल पर ट्रांसफर करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:377
msgid "Process the :ref:`payment <pos/restaurant/bills/payment>`."
msgstr ":ref:`पेमेंट <pos/restaurant/bills/payment>` प्रोसेस करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:378
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-chevron-right` :guilabel:`Continue` and repeat the process "
