#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:45
msgid ""
"To use the UrbanPiper integration in a live production environment, ensure "
"the following requirements are satisfied:"
msgstr ""
"लाइव प्रॉडक्शन एनवायरमेंट में UrbanPiper इंटिग्रेशन का इस्तेमाल करने के लिए, सुनिश्चित करें "
"कि निम्नलिखित आवश्यकताएं पूरी होती हैं:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:48
msgid ""
"**UrbanPiper subscription:** A valid UrbanPiper subscription is mandatory."
msgstr "**UrbanPiper सब्सक्रिप्शन:** एक वैध UrbanPiper सब्सक्रिप्शन अनिवार्य है।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:51
msgid ""
"For any concerns or queries regarding your UrbanPiper subscription, please "
"reach out to the account manager linked to your Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"अपने UrbanPiper सब्सक्रिप्शन से संबंधित किसी भी चिंता या प्रश्न के लिए, कृपया अपने Odoo "
"डेटाबेस से जुड़े अकाउंट मैनेजर से संपर्क करें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:54
msgid "**Odoo requirements:**"
msgstr "**Odoo आवश्यकताएं:**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:56
msgid ""
"**Odoo subscription:** An active Odoo Enterprise subscription is required. "
"Odoo Community does not support this integration."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo सब्सक्रिप्शन:** एक सक्रिय Odoo Enterprise सब्सक्रिप्शन आवश्यक है। Odoo कम्युनिटी "
"इस इंटिग्रेशन का समर्थन नहीं करती है।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:58
msgid "**Odoo version:** Odoo Enterprise version 18.0 or above."
msgstr "**Odoo वर्शन:** Odoo Enterprise वर्शन 18.0 या उससे ऊपर।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:59
msgid ""
"**Odoo platform:** All Odoo platforms are supported, including Odoo Online, "
"Odoo.sh, and On-Premise installations."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo प्लेटफ़ॉर्म:** सभी Odoo प्लेटफ़ॉर्म समर्थित हैं, जिसमें Odoo ऑनलाइन, Odoo.sh, और "
"On-Premise इंस्टॉलेशन शामिल हैं।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/online_food_delivery.rst:62
msgid ""
"**Delivery platform reseller account:** A registered reseller account is "
"required with each delivery platform to be integrated (e.g., Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."
msgstr ""
"**डिलीवरी प्लेटफ़ॉर्म रीसेलर अकाउंट:** एकीकृत किए जाने वाले प्रत्येक डिलीवरी प्लेटफ़ॉर्म (जैसे "
"Uber Eats, DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato) के साथ एक पंजीकृत रीसेलर अकाउंट "
