"On the payment screen, set a customer and select :guilabel:`Ship Later`."
msgstr ""
"पेमेंट स्क्रीन पर, एक ग्राहक सेट करें और :guilabel:`बाद में शिप करें` चुनें।"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:82
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, set a shipping date and click :guilabel:`Confirm` to "
